[{"Code":"en","Title":"Sending payouts via APIs","Slug":"documentation-template-7","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">Your Xendit Global Account automatically enables you to use our payout APIs across all supported corridors.</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-fcwwvj-748\">To payout to a particular corridor via APIs, you need to check: </p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-nlqudd-753\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-h9wr8w-754\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-b9vtmj-749\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-2\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Your business is eligible to make payouts from the currency balance</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-wurw4x-755\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-olntig-750\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-5#payout-capabilities\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">The interface is supported for the particular corridor</a></p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-hkw4ti-751\">Your business should use the right API for your payout type:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"884\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:884px;width:884px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:176px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\"><p data-block-id=\"79cb2111-6d35-4d4f-b3f9-a0cedc7f8b38\">Type of API</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"94353891-c86f-4c57-8867-d76b6b6fbb77\">Eligible payment types</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9a0629da-e09d-4c68-978a-254df0d98a05\">Availability</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uu5ow-kkb8ok-759\">Supported corridors</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"2783a2f5-64bd-4682-b9eb-f2a258919cfc\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-via-api\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Payout APIs</a> (Please only use v3 for regional accounts)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"16f58514-cb94-4d72-940e-f52e20ca93a8\">For <strong>first party</strong> payments such as:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uut71-7ph5fm-766\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uut71-vl3vba-767\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-waeo3m-762\">Vendor Payment</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uuupj-g386gi-768\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-cv1qtc-763\">Payroll</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uuwbm-xmdjm8-769\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-llr8hz-764\">Refund</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f6d5dc5-754e-4406-b1db-6a7c50a80415\">Available to all customers by default on the Global Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-89qshu-807\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-zohb94-808\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-z7m1yb-809\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-indonesia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Indonesia</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-fzmbox-810\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0h-o78fwb-801\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-philippines\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Philippines</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-gmagxq-811\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-m51hys-802\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-malaysia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Malaysia</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-k085vt-812\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-sn19hl-803\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-thailand\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Thailand</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-apmc0g-813\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-c7bv6i-804\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-vietnam\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Vietnam</a></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-c7bv6i-804\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-f8sa5w-805\">Follow the links for more detailed information about settlement time, minimum and maximum amounts for each payout channel</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvscc-9lvils-798\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/cross-border-payouts-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Cross border payout APIs</a></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvscc-taqw4j-799\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"69a84920-1f6b-4609-aef1-c0168eda3fa7\">For <strong>third party</strong> payments such as:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uvbbc-s5qpfy-781\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uvbbc-8r9jpx-782\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uv6k1-i67a29-779\">Last Mile Cross Border Payout</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"e374ea06-4c42-4b6f-b2f3-c86d113d5bfe\">Available only to licensed remittance companies</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvm50-km6urv-797\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvkc6-lv3qmd-795\">Not available by default on the Global Account. Please contact <a href=\"mailto:help@xendit.co\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">help@xendit.co</a> for assistance</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvkc6-aoiavt-796\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uzdz8-6vxi8v-840\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uzdz8-qkyq83-841\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-hrce6w-829\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-indonesia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Indonesia</a></p></li></ul><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uza31-gzf3hd-827\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-wzyaea-830\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-82qo4b-831\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-philippines\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Philippines</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-sjq2m9-834\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-xonnoy-835\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-thailand\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Thailand</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-3asxhz-836\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-fx8jmh-837\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-vietnam\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Vietnam</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-3asxhz-836\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-fx8jmh-837\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-singapore\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Singapore</a></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-977ed2-838\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-pqw8rw-839\">Follow the links for more detailed information about settlement time, minimum and maximum amounts for each payout channel</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"04e567e3-7a10-405e-b6e6-7655a93215e6\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Sending payouts via APIs","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Pengiriman Payouts melalui API","Slug":"documentation-template-7","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">Akun regional Xendit Anda secara otomatis memungkinkan Anda untuk menggunakan API payout kami di semua koridor yang didukung.</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-fcwwvj-748\">Untuk melakukan payout ke koridor tertentu melalui API, Anda perlu memeriksa: </p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-nlqudd-753\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-h9wr8w-754\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-b9vtmj-749\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-2\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Bisnis Anda memenuhi syarat untuk melakukan payout dari saldo mata uang</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-wurw4x-755\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-olntig-750\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-5#payout-capabilities\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Antarmuka didukung untuk koridor tertentu</a></p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-hkw4ti-751\">Bisnis Anda harus menggunakan API yang tepat untuk jenis payout Anda:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"884\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:884px;width:884px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:176px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\"><p data-block-id=\"79cb2111-6d35-4d4f-b3f9-a0cedc7f8b38\">Jenis API</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"94353891-c86f-4c57-8867-d76b6b6fbb77\">Jenis pembayaran yang memenuhi syarat</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9a0629da-e09d-4c68-978a-254df0d98a05\">Ketersediaan</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uu5ow-kkb8ok-759\">Koridor yang didukung</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"2783a2f5-64bd-4682-b9eb-f2a258919cfc\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-via-api\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Payout APIs</a> (Harap hanya gunakan v3 untuk akun regional)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"16f58514-cb94-4d72-940e-f52e20ca93a8\">Untuk pembayaran <strong>pihak pertama</strong> seperti:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uut71-7ph5fm-766\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uut71-vl3vba-767\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-waeo3m-762\">Pembayaran Vendor</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uuupj-g386gi-768\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-cv1qtc-763\">Penggajian</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uuwbm-xmdjm8-769\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-llr8hz-764\">Refund</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f6d5dc5-754e-4406-b1db-6a7c50a80415\">Tersedia untuk semua pelanggan secara default di akun regional</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-89qshu-807\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-zohb94-808\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-z7m1yb-809\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-indonesia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Indonesia</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-fzmbox-810\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0h-o78fwb-801\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-philippines\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Philippines</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-gmagxq-811\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-m51hys-802\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-malaysia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Malaysia</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-k085vt-812\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-sn19hl-803\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-thailand\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Thailand</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-apmc0g-813\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-c7bv6i-804\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-vietnam\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Vietnam</a></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-c7bv6i-804\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-f8sa5w-805\">Ikuti tautan untuk informasi lebih rinci tentang waktu penyelesaian, jumlah minimum dan maksimum untuk setiap channel payout</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvscc-9lvils-798\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/cross-border-payouts-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Cross border payout APIs</a></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvscc-taqw4j-799\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"69a84920-1f6b-4609-aef1-c0168eda3fa7\">Untuk pembayaran <strong>pihak ketiga</strong> seperti:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uvbbc-s5qpfy-781\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uvbbc-8r9jpx-782\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uv6k1-i67a29-779\">Last Mile Cross Border Payout</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"e374ea06-4c42-4b6f-b2f3-c86d113d5bfe\">Hanya tersedia untuk perusahaan pengiriman uang berlisensi</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvm50-km6urv-797\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvkc6-lv3qmd-795\">Tidak tersedia secara default di akun regional. Silakan hubungi <a href=\"mailto:help@xendit.co\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">help@xendit.co</a> untuk bantuan</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvkc6-aoiavt-796\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uzdz8-6vxi8v-840\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uzdz8-qkyq83-841\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-hrce6w-829\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-indonesia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Indonesia</a></p></li></ul><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uza31-gzf3hd-827\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-wzyaea-830\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-82qo4b-831\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-philippines\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Philippines</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-sjq2m9-834\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-xonnoy-835\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-thailand\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Thailand</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-3asxhz-836\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-fx8jmh-837\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-vietnam\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Vietnam</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-3asxhz-836\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-fx8jmh-837\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-singapore\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Singapore</a></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-977ed2-838\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-pqw8rw-839\">Ikuti tautan untuk informasi lebih rinci tentang waktu penyelesaian, jumlah minimum dan maksimum untuk setiap channel payout</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"04e567e3-7a10-405e-b6e6-7655a93215e6\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Pengiriman Payouts melalui API","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"การส่ง Payouts ผ่าน API","Slug":"documentation-template-7","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">บัญชี Xendit Global Account ของคุณจะเปิดใช้งานให้คุณสามารถใช้ payout APIs ของเราได้โดยอัตโนมัติในทุก corridors ที่รองรับ</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-fcwwvj-748\">ในการทำ Payout ไปยัง corridor ที่ต้องการผ่าน APIs คุณจำเป็นต้องตรวจสอบ: </p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-nlqudd-753\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-h9wr8w-754\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-b9vtmj-749\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-2\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">ธุรกิจของคุณมีสิทธิ์ในการทำ Payout จากยอดคงเหลือของสกุลเงินนั้น</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-wurw4x-755\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-olntig-750\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-5#payout-capabilities\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">interface ได้รับการรองรับสำหรับ corridor นั้นๆ</a></p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-hkw4ti-751\">ธุรกิจของคุณควรใช้ API ที่เหมาะสมสำหรับประเภท Payout ของคุณ:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"884\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:884px;width:884px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:176px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\"><p data-block-id=\"79cb2111-6d35-4d4f-b3f9-a0cedc7f8b38\">ประเภทของ API</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"94353891-c86f-4c57-8867-d76b6b6fbb77\">ประเภทการชำระเงินที่เข้าเกณฑ์</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9a0629da-e09d-4c68-978a-254df0d98a05\">ความพร้อมใช้งาน</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uu5ow-kkb8ok-759\">Corridors ที่รองรับ</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"2783a2f5-64bd-4682-b9eb-f2a258919cfc\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-via-api\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Payout APIs</a> (โปรดใช้ v3 สำหรับ regional accounts เท่านั้น)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"16f58514-cb94-4d72-940e-f52e20ca93a8\">สำหรับการชำระเงินแบบ <strong>first party</strong> เช่น:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uut71-7ph5fm-766\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uut71-vl3vba-767\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-waeo3m-762\">Vendor Payment</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uuupj-g386gi-768\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-cv1qtc-763\">Payroll</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uuwbm-xmdjm8-769\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-llr8hz-764\">Refund</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f6d5dc5-754e-4406-b1db-6a7c50a80415\">มีให้ลูกค้าทุกคนใช้งานได้โดยค่าเริ่มต้นบน Global Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-89qshu-807\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-zohb94-808\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-z7m1yb-809\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-indonesia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">อินโดนีเซีย</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-fzmbox-810\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0h-o78fwb-801\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-philippines\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">ฟิลิปปินส์</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-gmagxq-811\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-m51hys-802\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-malaysia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">มาเลเซีย</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-k085vt-812\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-sn19hl-803\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-thailand\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">ไทย</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-apmc0g-813\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-c7bv6i-804\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-vietnam\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">เวียดนาม</a></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-c7bv6i-804\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-f8sa5w-805\">ดูลิงก์เพื่อดูข้อมูลโดยละเอียดเพิ่มเติมเกี่ยวกับเวลาการชำระเงิน (settlement time), จำนวนเงินขั้นต่ำและสูงสุดสำหรับแต่ละช่องทางการทำ Payout</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvscc-9lvils-798\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/cross-border-payouts-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Cross border payout APIs</a></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvscc-taqw4j-799\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"69a84920-1f6b-4609-aef1-c0168eda3fa7\">สำหรับการชำระเงินแบบ <strong>third party</strong> เช่น:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uvbbc-s5qpfy-781\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uvbbc-8r9jpx-782\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uv6k1-i67a29-779\">Last Mile Cross Border Payout</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"e374ea06-4c42-4b6f-b2f3-c86d113d5bfe\">มีให้เฉพาะบริษัทโอนเงินที่ได้รับอนุญาตเท่านั้น</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvm50-km6urv-797\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvkc6-lv3qmd-795\">ไม่พร้อมใช้งานโดยค่าเริ่มต้นบน Global Account โปรดติดต่อ <a href=\"mailto:help@xendit.co\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">help@xendit.co</a> เพื่อขอความช่วยเหลือ</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvkc6-aoiavt-796\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uzdz8-6vxi8v-840\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uzdz8-qkyq83-841\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-hrce6w-829\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-indonesia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">อินโดนีเซีย</a></p></li></ul><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uza31-gzf3hd-827\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-wzyaea-830\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-82qo4b-831\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-philippines\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">ฟิลิปปินส์</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-sjq2m9-834\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-xonnoy-835\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-thailand\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">ไทย</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-3asxhz-836\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-fx8jmh-837\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-vietnam\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">เวียดนาม</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-3asxhz-836\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-fx8jmh-837\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-singapore\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">สิงคโปร์</a></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-977ed2-838\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-pqw8rw-839\">ดูลิงก์เพื่อดูข้อมูลโดยละเอียดเพิ่มเติมเกี่ยวกับเวลาการชำระเงิน (settlement time), จำนวนเงินขั้นต่ำและสูงสุดสำหรับแต่ละช่องทางการทำ Payout</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"04e567e3-7a10-405e-b6e6-7655a93215e6\"></p>","SeoTitle":"การส่ง Payouts ผ่าน API","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Envío de Payouts a través de APIs","Slug":"documentation-template-7","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">Su cuenta regional de Xendit le permite automáticamente usar nuestras API de Payout en todos los corredores compatibles.</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-fcwwvj-748\">Para realizar un Payout a un corredor en particular a través de API, usted necesita verificar: </p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-nlqudd-753\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-h9wr8w-754\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-b9vtmj-749\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-2\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Su comercio es elegible para realizar Payouts desde el Saldo de Moneda</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4ursdy-wurw4x-755\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-olntig-750\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-5#payout-capabilities\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">La interfaz es compatible con el corredor en particular</a></p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mc4urkiz-hkw4ti-751\">Su comercio debe usar la API correcta para su tipo de Payout:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"884\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:884px;width:884px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:176px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\"><p data-block-id=\"79cb2111-6d35-4d4f-b3f9-a0cedc7f8b38\">Tipo de API</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"94353891-c86f-4c57-8867-d76b6b6fbb77\">Tipos de Pago elegibles</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9a0629da-e09d-4c68-978a-254df0d98a05\">Disponibilidad</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uu5ow-kkb8ok-759\">Corredores compatibles</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"2783a2f5-64bd-4682-b9eb-f2a258919cfc\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-via-api\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">API de Payout</a> (Por favor, solo use la v3 para cuentas regionales)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"16f58514-cb94-4d72-940e-f52e20ca93a8\">Para Pagos de <strong>primera parte</strong> como:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uut71-7ph5fm-766\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uut71-vl3vba-767\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-waeo3m-762\">Pago a Proveedor</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uuupj-g386gi-768\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-cv1qtc-763\">Nómina</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uuwbm-xmdjm8-769\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uuifv-llr8hz-764\">Reembolso</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f6d5dc5-754e-4406-b1db-6a7c50a80415\">Disponible para todos los Clientes por defecto en la cuenta regional</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-89qshu-807\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-zohb94-808\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-z7m1yb-809\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-indonesia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Indonesia</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-fzmbox-810\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0h-o78fwb-801\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-philippines\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Filipinas</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-gmagxq-811\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-m51hys-802\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-malaysia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Malasia</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-k085vt-812\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-sn19hl-803\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-thailand\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Tailandia</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uw3h5-apmc0g-813\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-c7bv6i-804\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-vietnam\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Vietnam</a></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-c7bv6i-804\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvz0i-f8sa5w-805\">Siga los enlaces para obtener información más detallada sobre el tiempo de Liquidación, Montos mínimos y máximos para cada Canal de Payout</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"176\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvscc-9lvils-798\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/cross-border-payouts-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">API de Payout transfronterizo</a></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvscc-taqw4j-799\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"69a84920-1f6b-4609-aef1-c0168eda3fa7\">Para Pagos de <strong>tercera parte</strong> como:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uvbbc-s5qpfy-781\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uvbbc-8r9jpx-782\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uv6k1-i67a29-779\">Payout Transfronterizo de Última Milla</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\" style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"e374ea06-4c42-4b6f-b2f3-c86d113d5bfe\">Disponible solo para compañías de remesas con licencia</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvm50-km6urv-797\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvkc6-lv3qmd-795\">No está disponible por defecto en la cuenta regional. Por favor, contacte a <a href=\"mailto:help@xendit.co\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">help@xendit.co</a> para obtener asistencia</p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uvkc6-aoiavt-796\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uzdz8-6vxi8v-840\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uzdz8-qkyq83-841\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-hrce6w-829\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-indonesia\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Indonesia</a></p></li></ul><ul data-block-id=\"mc4uza31-gzf3hd-827\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-wzyaea-830\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-82qo4b-831\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-philippines\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Filipinas</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-sjq2m9-834\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-xonnoy-835\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-thailand\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Tailandia</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-3asxhz-836\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-fx8jmh-837\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-vietnam\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Vietnam</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-3asxhz-836\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-fx8jmh-837\"><a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/payouts-singapore\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Singapur</a></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-977ed2-838\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4uza32-pqw8rw-839\">Siga los enlaces para obtener información más detallada sobre el tiempo de Liquidación, Montos mínimos y máximos para cada Canal de Payout</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"04e567e3-7a10-405e-b6e6-7655a93215e6\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Envío de Payouts a través de APIs","Description":null}]